by-the-lack-of-a-margin-of-safety", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 15:19:32"}, {"id": "4741709", "title": "Meituan: Upside Remains Attractive Due To Strong EBITDA Growth Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up of woman receiving take away food delivery\" data-id=\"1149029916\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1005px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">10'000 Hours</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>I gave a buy rating to Meituan (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MPNGF\" title=\"Meituan\">OTCPK:MPNGF</a>) in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718819-meituan-sound-fundamentals-despite-a-weak-macro-backdrop\">September</a>, with my key thesis being that growth should remain robust as the business fundamentals are strong and the macro environment will recover eventually. Indeed, the stock has</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1149029916/image_1149029916.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741709-meituan-upside-remains-attractive-due-to-strong-ebitda-growth-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 15:14:20"}, {"id": "4741705", "title": "Zscaler: Near-Term Prospects Continue To Deteriorate", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digital security and privacy background. Cyber and crypto security shield on futuristic screen technology background.\" data-id=\"1972286424\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>While Zscaler (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZS\" title=\"Zscaler, Inc.\">ZS</a></span>) beat guidance in the first quarter and reported strong bookings growth, guidance and billings point towards a further growth slowdown. Net customer additions were also extremely weak during the quarter, which is somewhat concerning given that the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1972286424/image_1972286424.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741705-zscaler-stock-near-term-prospects-continue-to-deteriorate", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 15:05:53"}, {"id": "4741702", "title": "Coinbase: Crypto Hype With Still Too Much Uncertainties", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334406797/image_1334406797.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Maesot, Thailand- June 5, 2021:Bitcoin in front of Ripple XRP coin cryptocurrency is future online financial payment as digital money. Concept of Blockchain System Crisis.\" data-id=\"1334406797\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334406797/image_1334406797.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334406797/image_1334406797.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334406797/image_1334406797.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334406797/image_1334406797.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334406797/image_1334406797.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https:/